# Project State Management

The `.cursor/project-management/` directory is the **operational source of truth** for agent coordination.

---

## State Files

| File | Purpose |
|------|---------|
| `CURRENT_CONTEXT.md` | 30-second overview — read first |
| `PROJECT_STATUS.md` | Current phase, progress, active/blocked work |
| `TASKS.md` | Master task registry with statuses |
| `DECISIONS.md` | Decision index (complements `docs/adr/`) |
| `HANDOFF.md` | Agent-to-agent work transfer |

Strategic phases remain in `PROJECT_ROADMAP.md`. Full ADRs remain in `docs/adr/`.

---

## Before Work (Mandatory)

Every agent MUST read project state before starting any task:

1. `CURRENT_CONTEXT.md`
2. `PROJECT_STATUS.md`
3. `TASKS.md`
4. `DECISIONS.md`
5. `HANDOFF.md`
6. `PROJECT_ROADMAP.md`

**Never continue without understanding current context.**

Only after reading project state:

- Select Rules
- Select Skills
- Select Agent
- Select MCP

See `core/05-context-loading.mdc` and skill `context-loading`.

---

## During Work

Agents must:

- Update `TASKS.md` when task status changes
- Record important decisions in `DECISIONS.md`
- Create full ADR in `docs/adr/` for architectural decisions (per `architecture/06-adr.mdc`)
- Update `PROJECT_STATUS.md` when milestones or phase progress changes

---

## After Work (Mandatory)

Before finishing a session, agents MUST update:

| File | Required |
|------|----------|
| `PROJECT_STATUS.md` | Always |
| `TASKS.md` | Always |
| `HANDOFF.md` | Always |
| `CURRENT_CONTEXT.md` | Always |
| `DECISIONS.md` | When a decision was made |

Include in `HANDOFF.md`:

- What was completed
- Files changed
- Known issues
- Next recommended action for the following agent

---

## Source of Truth Hierarchy

When sources conflict, use this priority:

1. User instructions
2. Core Rules
3. Architecture Rules and ADRs (`docs/adr/`) — canonical for architecture
4. Project state files (`.cursor/project-management/`) — operational: tasks, handoffs, status
5. Domain Rules
6. Skills and Templates

`DECISIONS.md` is an index with links to full ADRs — never override `docs/adr/` content.

---

## Do Not Duplicate

| Existing System | Relationship |
|-----------------|--------------|
| `PROJECT_ROADMAP.md` | Strategic phases — do not merge into PROJECT_STATUS |
| `docs/adr/` | Full ADR documents — DECISIONS.md is index only |
| `docs/MEMORY.md` | Memory MCP conventions — not task tracking |
| Simple TODO lists | Replaced by TASKS.md |

